quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,logon ka hisaab ( aamaal ka waqt ) nazdeek aap_hncha hai aur woh ghaflat mein ( parre is se ) munh phair rahay hain
  21,2,un ke paas koi nai nasiyaat un ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se nahi aati magar woh usay khailtay hue suntay hain
  21,3,un ke dil ghaflat mein parre hue hain aur zalim log ( aapas mein ) chupkay chupkay baatein karte hain ke yeh ( shakhs kuch bhi ) nahi magar tumahray jaissa aadmi hai. to tum aankhon dekhte jaadoo ( ki lapait ) mein kyun atay ho
  21,4,( paighambar ne ) kaha ke jo baat aasman aur zameen mein ( kahi jati ) hai mera perwar-digaar usay jaanta hai. aur woh suneney wala ( aur ) jan-nay wala hai
  21,5,balkay ( zalim ) kehnay lagey ke ( yeh quran ) pareshan ( baatein hain jo ) khawab ( mein dekh li ) hain. ( nahi ) balkay is ne is ko apni taraf se bana liya hai ( nahi ) balkay ( yeh shair hai jo is ) shayar ( ka tatija ٴ taba ) hai. to jaisay pehlay ( paighambar nishanain day kar ) beje gay they ( isi terhan ) yeh bhi hamaray paas koi nishani laaye
  21,6,un se pehlay jin bustiyon ko hum ne halaakkiya woh imaan nahi latayen theen. tokiya yeh imaan le ayen ge
  21,7,aur hum ne tum se pehlay mard hi ( paighambar bana kar ) beje jin ki taraf hum wahi bhaijtay they. agar tum nahi jantay to jo yaad rakhtay hain un se pooch lau
  21,8,aur hum ne un ke liye aisay jism nahi banaye they ke khana nah khayen aur nah woh hamesha rehne walay they
  21,9,phir hum ne un ke baray mein ( apna ) wada sacha kardiya to un ko aur jis ko chaha nijaat di aur hadd se nikal jaane walon ko halaak kardiya
  21,10,hum ne tumhari taraf aisi kitaab nazil ki hai jis mein tumhara tazkara hai.kiya tum nahi samajte
